%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fab67616d0000b27388e3822cccfb8f2832c70c2e.jpg&a=w%3D160%26h%3D160%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&cd=2025-02-20T16%3A03%3A59\",\"srcSet\":\"/_gatsby/image/2d3d92e8b9b0c0b69f3d6bb7164ad3f4/04357339fb03853fa4c7c58c778afb21/ab67616d0000b27388e3822cccfb8f2832c70c2e.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Fback.thatmuch.fr%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fab67616d0000b27388e3822cccfb8f2832c70c2e.jpg&a=w%3D160%26h%3D160%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&cd=2025-02-20T16%3A03%3A59 160w,/_gatsby/image/2d3d92e8b9b0c0b69f3d6bb7164ad3f4/dc1aae889f240ccc4fd65b0cf8d56ac3/ab67616d0000b27388e3822cccfb8f2832c70c2e.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Fback.thatmuch.fr%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fab67616d0000b27388e3822cccfb8f2832c70c2e.jpg&a=w%3D320%26h%3D320%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&cd=2025-02-20T16%3A03%3A59 320w,/_gatsby/image/2d3d92e8b9b0c0b69f3d6bb7164ad3f4/9da802aab6120ae021c045c22e51e264/ab67616d0000b27388e3822cccfb8f2832c70c2e.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Fback.thatmuch.fr%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fab67616d0000b27388e3822cccfb8f2832c70c2e.jpg&a=w%3D640%26h%3D640%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&cd=2025-02-20T16%3A03%3A59 640w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":640,\"height\":640},\"alt\":\"Pochette de l'album Brat de Charlie XCX : fond vert éclatant, accompagné du titre en police pixelisée\",\"className\":\"wp-image-721 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"1\"}</script></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">L&#8217;album et son contexte</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Charli XCX, de son vrai nom Charlotte Emma Aitchison, est une artiste britannique reconnue pour son style pop avant-gardiste dit &#8220;hyper pop&#8221;. &#8220;BRAT&#8221;, son sixième album studio, explore des thèmes tels que l&#8217;identité, la rébellion et la croissance personnelle. L&#8217;album s&#8217;inspire du début des années 2000 et des raves des années 90 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brat_(album)\">1</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div data